# OmniRoute Cloud Worker — example secrets file.
#
# Copy this file to `.dev.vars` (for local dev with `wrangler dev`) or set
# the secret in production with `wrangler secret put CLOUD_SYNC_SECRET`.
#
# When deploying via the Cloudflare "Deploy to Workers" button, you do NOT
# need this file. Instead, after deploy, either:
#   - Use the OmniRoute /setup endpoint (recommended), OR
#   - Run: wrangler secret put CLOUD_SYNC_SECRET

# HMAC signing secret for response verification.
# The local OmniRoute instance must have the same value in
# OMNIROUTE_CLOUD_SYNC_SECRET (env var) or cloudSyncSecret (DB setting).
#
# Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32
CLOUD_SYNC_SECRET=

# Optional: comma-separated list of allowed upstream provider hosts.
# Empty = allow all.
# ALLOWED_UPSTREAM_HOSTS=api.openai.com,api.anthropic.com
